Package: FastQDesign
Type: Package
Title: scRNA-seq Experiment Design Tool
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yu", "Wang", , "yuw444@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Guide investigators in designing single-cell RNA sequencing experiments
    by shifting focus from UMI matrix back to raw FastQ reads. Includes
    the fastF C tool for pseudo-design dataset generation.
